data.revised_prompt: Craft a photorealistic image of a Southern Peach Smash cocktail. The drink should sit comfortably in a sturdy rocks glass, showcasing its golden-amber hue, while exposed to warm, diffused sunlight creating soft reflections. Embedded within the liquid are fresh mint leaves, exhibiting a deep green shade. A ripe peach slice graces the rim of the glass, providing a stark contrast against the cocktail's color. The backdrop is a slightly blurred, rustic wooden surface, amplifying the Southern charm and warmth. The cocktail embodies a fresh, summery elegance with an emphasis on texture and reflection. Please do not include any text or watermarks, and keep the background clear with a soft focus.
